Images and video can only be produced with blender 2.5 or higher.


BASIC TEST

You can produce images in /tmp/artifastring/images/  with:
  actions2images.py testfile.actions

For options, use
  actions2images.py --help


ENTIRE VIDEO

To produce the entire video, use
  actions2images.py testfile.actions
  actions2wav testfile.actions
  artifastring-movie.py testfile.wav

For options, use
  artifastring-movie.py --help

